    "description": "Join the Housing.com International Enterprises family as a Senior Software Engineer in Faridabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Housing.com International Enterprises:\nHousing.com International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Faridabad, Haryana, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Housing.com International Enterprises!",
